name: The Undertaker
overview: A detective leaves the force to take over the family business as an undertaker at the same time as he is being investigated for murder. His close encounters with corpses and his earlier police training lead him to see things some of his ex-colleagues miss and he investigates the crimes he encounters in an unofficial capacity often to the dismay of the official police.

episodes.name: Child Burial
episodes.overview: Luc is drawn into a new mystery when a coffin containing a baby skeleton turns up in a local art museum.

episodes.name: He Who Laughs Last
episodes.overview: The death of a clown leads Luc and friends to a strange circus.

episodes.name: The Heartless Corpse
episodes.overview: Luc receives a package with a human heart - another piece of the morbid puzzle he is confronting.

episodes.name: Slugfest
episodes.overview: Anna-Maria gets in the ring to investigate a local boxing champ's suspicious suicide.

episodes.name: Last Train
episodes.overview: Fabio and Erika discover a mummified corpse in a local antique shop.

episodes.name: Guilt and Expiation
episodes.overview: Luc's past comes back to haunt him as he confronts the mastermind behind the bone child plot.
